      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.5/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/180c137a-64f9-11e4-b736-5254006e85c2).  Ran 7 tests.  No failures.",
