      },
      "date": "2014-11-05 16:44:45.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nccc_internal.h shouldn't exist. I'd like to dump everything in it to vvp_internal.h.\n\nEventually ccc_ prefix should be removed in the client code.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
